        Sahayata Nepal (Help-Nepal) is a Non Governmental Organization, registered under the district administration office, Dhading (registration # 961/067-068) and affiliated with Social Welfare Council (affiliation # 30977). It is a non-profit making, non political and non sectarian organization working in the field of community development targeting marginalized and deprived communities. In 2010, a group of dedicated social workers form the different background came together with the vision of "healthy life in clean environment with educated and affluent society"". As a result, Sahayata Nepal came into existence and has been carrying out different activities with the approach of advocacy, awareness raising and social empowerment especially in thematic areas of Education, Health, Livelihood and Environment making coordination, collaboration and community mobilization as a vital tool.
