    <div id="collapseTwo" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordion">
        <div class="card-body">
        The overall goal of the organization is to support the government to promote community development through the coordination, collaboration and community mobilization approach of the local, national and international agencies. Taking into the consideration of this goal, the main objectives of the organization are:
        <ul>
            <li>
            To support for uplifting the livelihood of poor and marginalized families enabling them for income generating activities and increasing self employment opportunities with the family empowerment programs.
            </li>
            <li>
            To advocate on right of women and children and support them for their empowerment.
            </li>
            <li>
            To contribute on formal, technical and non formal education of poor, marginalized and deprived communities.
            </li>
            <li>
            To provide basic health services, RH / UP, child health service and education among the deprived people from the remote areas of Nepal.
            </li>
            <li>
            To lunch WASH related program.
            </li>
            <li>
            To support for successful implementation of government plan and programs.
            </li>
            <li>
            To contribute on the conservation of forestry, environment, climate change and global warming.</li>
        </ul>	 
